@startuml seq-rf02-consultar-lancamentos
title RF02 - Consultar lancamentos (especificado)

actor Comerciante as User
participant "API Gateway" as APIGW
participant "API Lancamentos" as ApiLanc
database "Aurora / PostgreSQL" as DB

User -> APIGW: GET /api/lancamentos?de=&ate=&tipo=\nBearer JWT
APIGW -> APIGW: Valida JWT\nlancamentos:read
APIGW -> ApiLanc: Encaminha

ApiLanc -> ApiLanc: Extrai merchantId do token
ApiLanc -> DB: SELECT * FROM lancamentos\nWHERE merchant_id = :merchant\nAND filtros + paginacao
DB --> ApiLanc: Pagina de resultados
ApiLanc --> APIGW: 200 OK { items, totalCount }
APIGW --> User: Lista de lancamentos

note over ApiLanc: Status POC: endpoint nao implementado

@enduml
